{
  "stem": "7904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Starting?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- there-- over there, I got a good-- a good place where to go to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The place of my work were 10-- 10 boys in the colony.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This means, you know, in the [? colony, ?] 10 boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to go by train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "About 50-- 50 kilometers by train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In a little town, a picuresque, a beautiful little town with the name Golcow, Golcow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Over there, the-- the Germans used to send in what they [INAUDIBLE] in-- in Europe, fish from Holland, wine, champagne from France, all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had it good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even the-- even the-- the security, was-- the police was good for [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Otherwise, we-- we didn't let him take home nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he used to go in-- in a room and sleep the whole-- the whole eight hours and we used to do whatever we wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we-- I worked-- we worked there about eight-- about 10 months, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From there, they opened another camp, concentration camp, Waldenburg, with the name Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Waldenburg is a big city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a big city, about 80,000, 85,000 Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the camp was out-- outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We used to go to work on a hill, on a-- not a big hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We used to, I was supposed to put up a factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] factory, this was-- I think it's synthetic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Synthetic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Synthetic gas or something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Wasn't bad, but we didn't have nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We used to go to work without-- without we used to lose our-- our strength day after day, day after day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But you know something, that I had in my mind that I'm gonna live through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
